{"type": "article", "id": 21362, "title": "谁把时尚杂志封面女郎画成了这样？！", "description": "粗线条，大色块，恶搞，又很萌。", "date": "2016-01-27T18:59:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2443, "name": "杂志"}, {"id": 191, "name": "漫画"}, {"id": 440, "name": "卡通"}, {"id": 12872, "name": "墨尔本"}, {"id": 760, "name": "艺术家"}, {"id": 22764, "name": "Stephen Baker"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 112, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606134932gczuw2809voLP3WF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t女性们在时尚杂志封面上拗着造型，她们还在摄影师的指导下，展现着一张张没有表情的脸。墨尔本艺术家<a href=\"http://www.stephenbakerart.com\" target=\"_blank\"> Stephen Baker </a>发现了这一点，<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/stephen-baker-magazine-covers-250116\" target=\"_blank\">最近，他开始手绘时尚杂志的封面</a>，绘画对象有 Kinfolk、VOGUE、Bazaar 等大牌杂志。在他的笔下，杂志封面女郎全都变成了没表情的卡通人物，粗线条、大色块，她们去除了性感，充满了萌感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134926JUSClrxoh3FH8NED.jpg\" title=\"AnOther Magazine 封面\" alt=\"AnOther Magazine 封面\" data-ratio=\"1.31491713\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>该艺术家绘制的 AnOther Magazine 封面，这是一本时尚摄影杂志，创刊于 2001 年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134926se4wVrEDojxTKhZW.jpg\" title=\"Kinfolk 封面\" alt=\"Kinfolk 封面\" data-ratio=\"1.2679558\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Kinfolk 杂志，生活方式季刊，2011 年创刊</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134926tm5scxuJaAzL1BPT.jpg\" title=\"Hunger 杂志\" alt=\"Hunger 杂志\" data-ratio=\"1.29281768\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Hunger 杂志，时尚半年刊</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061349273zYDQIMdJ6aniLqf.jpg\" title=\"Vogue 杂志\" alt=\"Vogue 杂志\" data-ratio=\"1.33425414\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Vogue 杂志</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134927kmU2XBCKqcA4PVEN.jpg\" title=\"Bazaar 杂志\" alt=\"Bazaar 杂志\" data-ratio=\"1.37983425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Bazaar </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134928ap2h75sdDJQCAe0T.jpg\" title=\"Champ 杂志\" alt=\"Champ 杂志\" data-ratio=\"1.29143646\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Champ 杂志</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134928R8sOrzDvPNEUGLw3.jpg\" title=\"Yen 杂志\" alt=\"Yen 杂志\" data-ratio=\"1.30939227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Yen 杂志，这是一本双月刊女性杂志</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tStephen Baker 是最近才对杂志封面感兴趣的。“一天的工作结束后，我会走出工作室买本时尚杂志回家，然后照着封面画一幅小画，这都快成了我的常规动作了。”在他的笔下，时尚的女性造型转化为一系列的抽象的、柔和的形状。色彩的光泽和画布的纹理相结合，很有趣。<span style=\"text-align:center;\">作为一名艺术家，</span><a href=\"http://www.stephenbakerart.com\" target=\"_blank\"> Stephen Baker </a><span style=\"text-align:center;\"> 的日常工作是这样的：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134929TFSywIQcxROvfhNp.jpg\" title=\"a \" alt=\"a \" data-ratio=\"0.627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134929vAhb7QUeHrNG3X8B.jpg\" title=\"a \" alt=\"a \" data-ratio=\"0.627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t而他的绘画风格也很稳定，简洁线条、多色彩：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134930iD9o8A7MpfVLhqnt.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134930m0k7Jwni8YSlyFEf.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134930ZPdjqt7wUicXW1Mo.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061349310Sxs9aPlB32AWJvM.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t他也在个人网站上贩卖自己的艺术品，如果你对他感兴趣，可以移步至<a href=\"http://www.stephenbakerstockroom.com\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/stephen-baker-magazine-covers-250116\" target=\"_blank\">itsnicethat</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}